3. Painite - 

 First discovered by English mineralogist Arthur C.D.  Pain in the 1950s in Myanmar, for many years, Painite has always been at the top of the list of the world's rarest gemstones with only 2 specimens found.


 Until 2005, scientists still found only 25 samples of Painite on the planet.  Therefore, the Guinness Book of Records recognized Painite as the most rare mineral in the world in 2005.

 Today, Painite is no longer as rare as it used to be.  It has been discovered a Painite mineral mine in Myanmar - where is considered the source of this stone.

 However, Painite is still on the list of the most precious minerals on Earth.  Therefore, the price of Painite is quite large - about..

4. PROVIDERâ€™s Issuing Bank will issue an MT-799 Pre-Advice by SWIFT MT-799 (Exhibit A) confirming that they are Ready, Willing and Able to issue the STAND BY LETTER OF CREDIT (SBLC) as per agreed verbiage (Exhibit C).

Man is foolish.

Many are deceived to believe the whites are wise. I ask you, will any wise person manufacture weapons that destroys lives? Knowing fully well that if you kill you must be killed and whatever you do to others must surely be done unto you. 

Let our test be drawn from Everlasting Gospel vol. 2 Chapter 71 vs 148 to 158

"THERE IS NO DIFFERENCE BETWEEN MAN AND AN ANIMAL; THE BLOOD OF A GOAT FOR AN INSTANCE IS EXACTLY LIKE THE BLOOD OF A HUMAN BEING. 
Brethren, human beings deserve pity because for no reason should the blood of an animal enter into the mouth of a human being.

God gave man power to rule over the different kinds of animals and he is regarded as god to all other creatures of God. The proof is in the fact that no matter how huge an animal may be, as soon as it sees a man, it becomes weak and may fall down.
Brethren, know that you will be forgiven of whatever sin that you commit except that when you kill a man you will in turn be killed.
That was the more reason that our Lord Jesus Christ asked Peter to put back his sword into the sheath and added that he who takes the sword must die by the sword.

You are always deceived into thinking that the whites are wise but I ask, if this is so why should they manufacture destructive weapons? He who knows God commits no murder.
Many people allege that it is because of unemployment that they enrol as soldiers. I am assuring you that your eyes will open one day when you kill somebody even in the battlefield, for you will also be killed. 
Christ has known that whatever a person does to the other, the same will be done to him, hence He admonishes us to refrain from all manners of sins so that these sins may not stand against us.

We yearn for an everlasting life, yet we refuse to abide by the instructions of the Holy Spirit.How would we then have everlasting life and peace? 

Brethren, man is foolish. Note that if we refuse to abide by the directives of the Holy Spirit, there is nothing we can do to be saved.
YOU MAY CLING TO THE SAYING THAT YOU ARE SAVED BY GRACE, NOTE THAT YOU WERE SAVED BY GRACE SO THAT YOU MAY REFRAIN FROM SIN AND BE ABLE TO SERVE GOD WILLINGLY, what shall we say then? Shall we continue in sin, that grace may abound? ".

We should put especially those who still eat meat and fish into fervent prayers. Wickedness has become too old in the societies to the extent it is now looked at as righteousness. It's painful when I see even medical doctors argue when you tell them eating of meat and fish is wrong.

A man once told me he has been practicing righteousness all his life during my gospel and when asked if he has not been eating meat and fish these years, he kept quiet.Then later said he didn't know it's unrighteous.

Two sisters were fighting over a meat and when asked what's the problem, one said the other should give her back her meat. When asked "her meat"? She thought over it and walked away without any more word.. Why? Because she imagined what she just said and probably pondered over what if it was actually her flesh that was being dragged.

When one isn't conscious enough to realise he is not being nice to God, to humanity or himself by killing or patronising killers how would he know what is good for his neighbor ?
People should stop arrogating their problems to their neighbors and love one another because the problems are caused by stubbornness and unrepentance from sin.

Let those who have ears hear.
